FuncDef: This command displays FDB entry for a given MAC address.

ParaDef.Info: Specifies the physical port identifier portion of the SAP definition.
Displays the SDP identifier. Values-1 to 17407.
Specifies to display information pertaining to the MAC address.

msg: Error CLI:fdb [ sap <sap-id> ] | [ sdp <sdp-id> ] | [ mac <ieee-address> ] | [ detail ]
Error CLI:fdb [ { all | mac <ieee-address> | sap <sap-id> | mesh-sdp <sdp-id> [ <:> vc <-> id ] | spoke-sdp <sdp-id> [ <:> vc- id ] | vxlan <-> instance <1> <...> <2> [ vtep <ip> <-> <address> ] }
